album.title: Sinatra Reprise: The Very Good Years

name: Love And Marriage
comments: It's not an illusion....easily separated! lol. Great Sinatra track.
Being associated with one of the best shows in the history of TV is not "doomed".
Sinatra is forever doomed to be linked with Married With Children because of this classic!
It's nice to be able to hear the full version of this song.
Everyone will hate me for saying this but this always sounds like a Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory oompa loompa song
love that i can be not yet 30 and this can still remind me of my childhood....
"Sorry, Peg, I didn't hear you. I was thinking of killing myself"
Every time I hear this it makes me smile!!! :)
